Product Description

Beatrix little kid pack: percival (dino) holds everything a tot needs for a busy day. Constructed from durable nylon and easy-to-clean laminated canvas these sturdy and cute looking bags have a large interior space containing a smaller zipped pocket a padded back panel and padded shoulder straps.
